text: Ani jara amhi tyancyavara he pharja (anivarya) kele asate ki svatahci hatya karuna ghya, kinva apalya gharatuna nighuna ja, tara tyancyapaiki phara thodyaca lokanni tyace palana kele asate. Ani jara he teca karatila jyaci tyanna sikavana dili jate tara niscitaca tyancyasathi phara cangale jhale asate ani khupa majabutice tharale asate
